org.quickserver.net.server
Interface ClientIdentifiable

public interface ClientIdentifiable

This is an interface that can be implemented by ClientData so that the client connected can be identified. One can search an client by using QuickServer.findFirstClientById(java.lang.String), QuickServer.findAllClientById(java.lang.String), QuickServer.findClientByKey(java.lang.String), QuickServer.findAllClientByKey(java.lang.String), QuickServer.findAllClient()

Since:
1.3.1
